reviewText: Was a bit weird for me but not unwatchable. I just like my sci fi a little more on the classic side. This one was much tripper than I'm used to. Also I have terrible hearing so closed captions is a must for me and this doesn't have captions at all. Lessons learned. There's a reason its cheap. No captioniong. Yuck for me, although I know this won't be a prob for most
